"$(3,167)", "bbox": [519.0, 1466.1, 575.2, 1483.8]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [651.3, 98.2, 674.8, 113.8]}, {"text": "Intersegment sales eliminate upon consolidation and are generally", "bbox": [688.8, 98.2, 1156.8, 113.8]}, {"text": "made at prices approximating those that the selling entity would be", "bbox": [688.8, 116.9, 1156.9, 132.5]}, {"text": "able to obtain in third-party transactions.", "bbox": [688.8, 135.7, 966.8, 151.3]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [651.3, 160.7, 674.8, 176.3]}, {"text": "The 2016 gain on sale of assets included the sale of Piceance and", "bbox": [688.8, 160.7, 1156.8, 176.3]}, {"text": "South Texas oil and gas properties. The 2014 amount represented", "bbox": [688.8, 179.4, 1156.9, 195.1]}, {"text": "the gain on sale of the Hugoton properties.", "bbox": [688.8, 198.2, 988.6, 213.8]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [651.3, 223.2, 673.9, 238.8]}, {"text": "The 2015 amount included approximately $1.6 billion of impairment", "bbox": [688.8, 223.2, 1156.9, 238.8]}, {"text": "and related charges associated with non-core domestic oil and gas", "bbox": [688.8, 242.0, 1156.9, 257.6]}, {"text": "assets in the Williston Basin (sold in November 2015) and Piceance", "bbox": [688.8, 260.7, 1156.9, 276.3]}, {"text": "Basin sold in March 2016. The remaining 2015 charges were mainly", "bbox": [688.8, 279.5, 1156.9, 295.1]}, {"text": "associated with the decline in commodity prices and management", "bbox": [688.8, 298.2, 1156.8, 313.8]}, {"text": "changes to future development plans. The 2014 amount was mainly", "bbox": [688.8, 317.0, 1156.9, 332.6]}, {"text": "comprised of impairment and related charges on the Williston and", "bbox": [688.8, 335.7, 1156.9, 351.4]}, {"text": "Piceance assets.", "bbox": [688.8, 354.5, 807.0, 370.1]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [651.3, 379.5, 674.8, 395.1]}, {"text": "The 2016 amount included a net charge of $61 million related to the", "bbox": [688.8, 379.5, 1156.9, 395.1]}, {"text": "sale of Libya and exit from Iraq. The 2015 amount included", "bbox": [688.8, 398.2, 1156.8, 413.9]}, {"text": "impairment and related charges of approximately $1.7 billion for", "bbox": [688.8, 417.0, 1156.9, 432.6]}, {"text": "operations where Occidental exited or reduced its involvement in and", "bbox": [688.8, 435.8, 1156.9, 451.4]}, {"text": "$3.4 billion related to the decline in commodity prices.", "bbox": [688.8, 454.5, 1064.2, 470.1]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [651.3, 479.5, 674.8, 495.2]}, {"text": "The 2016 amount included the gain on sale of the Occidental Tower", "bbox": [688.8, 479.5, 1156.9, 495.2]}, {"text": "in Dallas and a non-core specialty chemicals business. The 2015", "bbox": [688.8, 498.3, 1156.9, 513.9]}, {"text": "amount represented a gain on sale of an idled facility.", "bbox": [688.8, 517.0, 1062.2, 532.7]}, {"text": "(f)", "bbox": [651.3, 542.0, 670.4, 557.7]}, {"text": "The 2014 amount included a $633 million gain on sale of Occidental’s", "bbox": [688.8, 542.0, 1156.9, 557.7]}, {"text": "interest in BridgeTex Pipeline Company, LLC, and a $1.4 billion gain", "bbox": [688.8, 560.8, 1156.9, 576.4]}, {"text": "on sale of a portion of Occidental’s investment in Plains Pipeline.", "bbox": [688.8, 579.6, 1140.3, 595.2]}, {"text": "(g)", "bbox": [651.3, 604.6, 674.8, 620.2]}, {"text": "The 2016 amount included charges related to the termination of crude", "bbox": [688.8, 604.6, 1156.9, 620.2]}, {"text": "oil supply contracts.The 2015 amount included an impairment charge", "bbox": [688.8, 623.3, 1156.9, 638.9]}, {"text": "of $814 million related to the Century gas processing plant as a result", "bbox": [688.8, 642.1, 1156.9, 657.7]}, {"text": "of SandRidge’s inability to provide volumes to the plant and meet its", "bbox": [688.8, 660.8, 1156.9, 676.5]}, {"text": "contractual obligations to deliver CO2.", "bbox": [688.8, 679.6, 954.3, 696.1]}, {"text": "(h)", "bbox": [651.3, 704.6, 674.7, 720.2]}, {"text": "The 2016 amount included charges of $541 million related to a", "bbox": [688.8, 704.6, 1156.9, 720.2]}, {"text": "reserve for doubtful accounts and $78 million loss on the distribution", "bbox": [688.8, 723.4, 1156.9, 739.0]}, {"text": "of the remaining CRC stock. The 2015 amount included a $227 million", "bbox": [688.8, 742.1, 1156.9, 757.7]}, {"text": "other-than-temporary loss on Occidental’s investment in California", "bbox": [688.8, 760.9, 1156.8, 776.5]}, {"text": "Resources. The 2014 amount included an $805 million impairment", "bbox": [688.8, 779.6, 1156.9, 795.2]}, {"text": "charge for the Joslyn oil sand project and a $553 million other-than-", "bbox": [688.8, 798.4, 1152.6, 814.0]}, {"text": "temporary loss on the investment in California Resources.", "bbox": [688.8, 817.1, 1089.3, 832.8]}, {"text": "(i)", "bbox": [651.3, 842.1, 669.5, 857.8]}, {"text": "Represents amounts attributable to income from continuing", "bbox": [688.8, 842.1, 1156.8, 857.8]}, {"text": "operations after deducting a non controlling interest amount of $14", "bbox": [688.8, 860.9, 1156.9, 876.5]}, {"text": "million in 2014. The non controlling interest amount has been netted", "bbox": [688.8, 879.6, 1156.9, 895.3]}, {"text": "in the midstream and marketing segment earnings.", "bbox": [688.8, 898.4, 1040.7, 914.0]}, {"text": "(j)", "bbox": [651.3, 923.4, 669.5, 939.0]}, {"text": "The 2016 and 2015 amounts included gains related to the Ecuador", "bbox": [688.8, 923.4, 1156.8, 939.0]}, {"text": "settlement. See Note 2 of the consolidated financial statements. The", "bbox": [688.8, 942.2, 1156.9, 957.8]}, {"text": "2014 amount included the results of Occidental's California", "bbox": [688.8, 960.9, 1156.8, 976.6]}, {"text": "operations.", "bbox": [688.8, 979.7, 766.1, 995.3]}, {"text": "Oil and Gas", "bbox": [651.3, 1026.1, 757.9, 1046.9]}, {"text": "(in millions)", "bbox": [657.6, 1068.1, 739.6, 1087.9]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [962.5, 1068.1, 998.6, 1087.9]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [1033.3, 1068.1, 1069.4, 1087.9]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1104.2, 1068.1, 1140.3, 108